### Kafka Topics
- `task-events` - Task lifecycle events (created/updated/completed/deleted)
- `reminders` - Scheduled reminder notifications
- `task-updates` - Real-time updates (future)

### Microservices
- `frontend` - Next.js UI
- `backend` (chat-api) - FastAPI + Dapr events
- `notification-service` - Consumes reminders
- `recurring-service` - Creates recurring task occurrences

